<plot>Knights of Atomikaron introduces us to Sir OMG and F12 of Gigamore, two oddball characters in an elaborate role-playing game carried out by a close-knit group of men. Riffing on a number of contemporary documentaries, this mockumentary ventures into the men's lives as they convey their private thoughts, hopes and greatest fears.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?294677</url></doc>
